<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Request Library SSRF</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F2EFEB 0%, #918B83 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(48, 44, 42, 0.2);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F2120C 0%, #3C1053 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .form-section {
            background: #F2EFEB;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .form-section h2 {
            color: #3C1053;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #302C2A;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #918B83;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .form-group input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #3C1053;
        }
        .btn {
            background: #3C1053;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #B51825;
        }
        .result-section {
            background: #302C2A;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .result-section h3 {
            color: #F2120C;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .result-content {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            overflow-x: auto;
            max-height: 400px;
        }
        .error {
            color: #F2120C;
        }
        .success {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .hint {
            background: #918B83;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .hint h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #F2EFEB;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #3C1053;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            color: #B51825;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üì° Request Library SSRF</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
            
            <div class="form-section">
                <h2>Test Request Library SSRF</h2>
                <p>This endpoint uses the 'request' library which can be vulnerable to different attack vectors.</p>
                
                <form method="POST">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="url">Target URL:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="url" name="url" placeholder="http://example.com" value="<%= url || '' %>">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn">Make Request</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <% if (url) { %>
                <div class="result-section">
                    <h3>Request Result</h3>
                    <p><strong>Target URL:</strong> <%= url %></p>
                    
                    <% if (error) { %>
                        <div class="error">
                            <strong>Error:</strong> <%= error %>
                        </div>
                    <% } else if (result) { %>
                        <div class="success">
                            <strong>Response:</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="result-content"><%= result %></div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="hint">
                <h4>üí° Hint</h4>
                <p>The request library may handle different protocols differently. Try various internal services and protocols!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
